    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Tools</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The external tools used to build, profile, reverse-engineer, and document EmulatR. None of these are required to run the emulator; they are the developer-side toolchain behind the project.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">In this section</para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="NotesBox" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Ghidra -- reverse-engineering the decompressed SRM firmware.</li>
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Help &amp; Manual -- the authoring tool that produces this documentation.</li>
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Software Verify -- the Performance Validator profiler used to find hot spots.</li>
      <li styleclass="NotesBox">Qt Creator -- the IDE and CMake build environment.</li>
    </list>
